OL,6,FA man who kept his dead father's body
OL,7,Fin a fridge at their family home in
OL,8,FLondonderry has been sentenced to
OL,9,Fthree years, with 18 months to be in
OL,10,Fprison.
OL,12,FThe 86-year-old was found wrapped
OL,13,Finside a duvet and plastic sheet in
OL,14,FJuly 2024.
OL,16,FLondonderry Crown Court heard that his
OL,17,Fson, John Garrett O'Sullivan, 56 of
OL,18,FCulmore Road, did not alert the
OL,19,Fauthorities because he was worried
OL,20,Fthat he would become homeless after
OL,21,Fhis father died.
