OL,6,FNoel O'Sullivan, 86, was a retired
OL,7,Forthodontist. His son was jailed for
OL,8,Fpreventing a lawful burial in July
OL,9,F2024.
OL,11,FPolice forced their way into the
OL,12,Ffamily home on 17 July 2024 after
OL,13,Freceiving a 999 call from one of Mr
OL,14,FO'Sullivan's daughters who was
OL,15,Fconcerned for her father's safety.
OL,17,FInside officers noticed an odour and
OL,18,Fmade the gruesome discovery.
