OL,6,FHowever, the judge accepted that
OL,7,FO'Sullivan was motivated by self
OL,8,Fpreservation that he may lose his home.
OL,10,FThe court was told the PHD graduate
OL,11,Fhad been living in the garage of the
OL,12,Ffamily property after having a nervous
OL,13,Fbreakdown in 1997.
OL,15,FO'Sullivan told police his father had
OL,16,Fbeen ill and he tried to help him but
OL,17,Fthe next day he was dead and he
OL,18,Fresearched what the procedure was for
OL,19,Fa sudden death.
