OL,6,FIn a prepared statement to police, he
OL,7,Fdenied any wrong doing or mistreatment
OL,8,Fof his father.
OL,10,FThe date and cause of death are not
OL,11,Fknown.
OL,13,FJudge Roseanne McCormick K.C. told
OL,14,FO'Sullivan said he "prioritised his
OL,15,Fown to do list by not alerting anyone
OL,16,Fabout his father's death and pursued
OL,17,Fhis own agenda after his father's
OL,18,Fdeath".
